Settings for Linux, using the commercial Absoft Fortran compiler and the 
commercial Intel C++ compiler (icpc).

Requires the following environment settings:

ESMF_COMPILER absoftintel

The correct value of ESMF_F90_PTR_BASE_SIZE in 64-bit mode appears to be
compiler version dependent:
Absoft  8.x -> ESMF_F90_PTR_BASE_SIZE=48
Absoft  9.x -> ESMF_F90_PTR_BASE_SIZE=64
Absoft 10.x -> ESMF_F90_PTR_BASE_SIZE=72
